```

## Dataset

The 360UAV sequence root for the 5-sequence experiment is:

```text
/mnt/disk1/lanboyang/Datasets/360uav/seqs
```

Run all 5 sequences under this root unless the user gives a narrower sequence list.

## Result summary

After all sequences finish:

- Summarize the experiment results in a concise table.
- Include the sequence name, output path, status, and key metrics.
- Mark failed, missing, or incomplete runs explicitly.
- Include the tmux session name and any relevant log paths when reporting progress or failures.
